Package: textools
Type: Package
Title: an R toolbox for text mining tasks 
Date: 20/05/2020
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nicola Righetti
Maintainer: Nicola Righetti <info@nicolarighetti.net>
URL: https://github.com/nicolarighetti/textools
Description: A set of tools to perform text mining tasks. Mostly a convenience wrapper for well-established functions to perform common text mining tasks saving time and code.
